{"tid":296450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"每層樓1個廚房太多　2樓宜住哂澤鉅一家","createTime":"2017-06-24T14:44:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T18:19:25.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f09ebb418d3ce139e1b0493010995063686461cb","tid":296450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VuyRA9Llkps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVuyRA9Llkps&d=cQd7oYLqIARGyj0olsuPpm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=2567e50f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VuyRA9Llkps</a><br />\n<br />\n發佈日期：2017年6月24日<br />\n擁有20多年室內設計經驗、負責過不少豪宅項目的E F Design設計總監馮建耀(Eric)認為，李嘉誠大宅安排尚算合理。一般老人家會安排住地下層數，避免行樓梯，但大宅設有升降機，所以誠哥住頂層亦不添麻煩，更可擁有更開揚景觀。<br />\n<br />\n「可惜室外泳池形狀不太理想，但幸好泳池被大宅所遮擋，有私隱度。」全屋多處使用落地大玻璃，且景觀開揚，採光度十分充足。客廳面向哥爾夫球會，屬理想景觀。<br />\n<br />\n不過Eric指，誠哥有四位孫仔孫女，屋內娛樂看來不足。而由於有四人住地下一層，該層客廳公共空間亦比較少。此外，每層均設有廚房，則略嫌太多。<br />\n<br />\n他建議，地下可改成全層為客飯廳及廚房，大宅有訪客舉行party時，私人空間便不會被影響。而李澤鉅一家六口可住上層，有足夠空間可住曬六個人，「有時住得迫啲，一家人更顯親密和窩心。」他補充，屋內設計第一感覺源自入屋第一景觀，原來設計的地下客廳較小，如將房間往上移，放大客飯廳，感覺較為理想。<br />\n<br />\n其次，地下可以設置一個較大的廚房取代原來每層一個廚房，此舉可使睡房空間放大。他又建議，可於地下增設Bar Area，除了可招待訪客，有時還可與家人輕鬆小酌一杯。"},{"pid":"05bde6eb895f2dd98988e226808ef20b3841014a","tid":296450,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:46:03.000Z","msg":"住得迫d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56371a19bbaf2719034932730f3e6a28f79497ec","tid":296450,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:49:14.000Z","msg":"想知佢廚房會唔會有曱甴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40789d5e544720ff47714b0abd06c0dd50e77b81","tid":296450,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>住得迫d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n首富都住到咁，盡顯地產商本色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b732971b0c2c8117a7199ef3afa97ee9c6721f1","tid":296450,"uid":76117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:29:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b9ec94923524ed9262d07d401168f6bb9a34ba7","tid":296450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T15:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c899871a36c09e61faa628027ea87195f2030cf3","tid":296450,"uid":41944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:17:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫首富一家住得迫d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nfail<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"796ee90e13614f3caa237196afc9d19e9be6b5d5","tid":296450,"uid":104020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T18:27:53.000Z","msg":"洗撚你比意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e30f2b65ffe669a4fa36fb53a2eff5bf101355d6","tid":296450,"uid":82587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T06:02:18.000Z","msg":"屋內娛樂不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85641226bb8e8ace4e1bded4ad790105b889d5e","tid":296450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc5997d15fb81430fb0c2bdbcdbe5cf36c02521","tid":296450,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:14:39.000Z","msg":"窮撚批評有錢人既諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"